                throws NoMeasurementException
        Parameters:

        start - The start of the period.

      • getValue

        public Double getValue(Sensor sensor,
              Date start,
              Date end,
              Long gapSeconds)
                throws NoMeasurementException,
                       MeasurementGapException
        Parameters:
        sensor - The Sensor making the measurements.
        start - The start of the interval.
        end - The end of the interval
        gapSeconds - The maximum number of seconds that measurements need to be within the start and end.
        Returns:
        The value measured the difference between the end value and the start value.
        Throws:
        NoMeasurementException - if there are no measurements around the start or end time.
        MeasurementGapException - if the measurements around start or end are too far apart.
